      <title>Markdown Task-list(체크리스트) Plugin 설치하기</title>
      <link href="/2019/08/31/Markdown-Task-list-Plugin-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0/"/>
      <url>/2019/08/31/Markdown-Task-list-Plugin-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/54312678/64017723-4d44ca00-cb65-11e9-8726-b65dd9e655d1.JPG" alt="markdown"></p><h2 id="markdown-it-plus"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#markdown-it-plus"></a> Markdown-it-plus</h2><p>사실 아직까지도 Markdown과 Markdown-it-plus와의 차이점은 잘 모르겠습니다.<br>그런데 이 플러그인을 사용하는 사람이 많아서 그저 따라 설치했을 뿐인데 원하던 체크리스트를 간단히 추가할 수 있어서 다행이었습니다.</p><p>먼저 Markdown-it-plus 설치 방법부터 차근차근 알아봅시다.</p><br><h3 id="설치"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#설치"></a> 설치</h3><p>hexo가 설치된 폴더에서 명령어를 입력하세요.<br>저는 blog 폴더에 설치했습니다.</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd blog (hexo 설치 폴더로 이동)</span><br><span class="line">npm un hexo-renderer-markde --save  (기존의 markdown 삭제)</span><br><span class="line">npm i hexo-renderer-mardkdown-it-plus --save  (Markdown-it-plus 설치)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="설정"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#설정"></a> 설정</h3><p>hexo의   <code>_config.yml</code> 맨 밑에 다음과 같이 설정을 붙여 넣습니다.</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">markdown_it_plus:</span><br><span class="line">    highlight: true</span><br><span class="line">    html: true</span><br><span class="line">    xhtmlOut: true</span><br><span class="line">    breaks: true</span><br><span class="line">    langPrefix:</span><br><span class="line">    linkify: true</span><br><span class="line">    typographer:</span><br><span class="line">    quotes: “”‘’</span><br><span class="line">    pre_class: highlight</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>여기까지가 Markdown-it-plus 설치, 적용 방법입니다.<br>그러면 이제 본격적으로 Task-list를 향해 달려봅시다!</p><br><br><h2 id="markdown-it-task-lists"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#markdown-it-task-lists"></a> Markdown-it-task-lists</h2><p><a href="https://hann726.github.io/2019/08/31/markdown-%EB%AC%B8%EB%B2%95%EC%9D%84-%EC%95%8C%EC%95%84%EB%B3%B4%EC%9E%90/#%EC%B2%B4%ED%81%AC%EB%A6%AC%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8check-lists">Task-list</a>는 이전 포스팅에서 적용된 모습을 볼 수 있습니다.</p><h3 id="설치-2"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#설치-2"></a> 설치</h3><p>hexo가 설치 되어 있는 폴더에서 명령어를 입력합니다.</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install markdown-it-task-lists</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="설정-2"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#설정-2"></a> 설정</h3><p>hexo의 <code>_config.yml</code> 파일 Markdown-it-plus 부분에 plugin을 추가합니다.</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">markdown_it_plus:</span><br><span class="line">    highlight: true</span><br><span class="line">    html: true</span><br><span class="line">    xhtmlOut: true</span><br><span class="line">    breaks: true</span><br><span class="line">    langPrefix:</span><br><span class="line">    linkify: true</span><br><span class="line">    typographer:</span><br><span class="line">    quotes: “”‘’</span><br><span class="line">    pre_class: highlight</span><br><span class="line">    plugins:</span><br><span class="line">       - plugin:</span><br><span class="line">       name: markdown-it-task-lists</span><br><span class="line">       enable: true</span><br><span class="line">       options:</span><br><span class="line">       # this is plugin option</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><p>모든 설정 후 체크리스트를 만들어봅시다!</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">- [x] ~~markdown-it-plus~~</span><br><span class="line">- [x] ~~markdown-it-task-lists~~</span><br><span class="line">- [ ] markdown posting</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">1. [x] AA</span><br><span class="line">2. [ ] BB</span><br><span class="line">3. [ ] CC</span><br><span class="line">    1. [x] **DD**</span><br><span class="line">    1. [ ] FF</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul class="contains-task-list"><li class="task-list-item"><input class="task-list-item-checkbox" checked disabled type="checkbox"> <s>markdown-it-plus</s></li><li class="task-list-item"><input class="task-list-item-checkbox" checked disabled type="checkbox"> <s>markdown-it-task-lists</s></li><li class="task-list-item"><input class="task-list-item-checkbox" disabled type="checkbox"> markdown posting</li></ul><ol class="contains-task-list"><li class="task-list-item"><input class="task-list-item-checkbox" checked disabled type="checkbox"> AA</li><li class="task-list-item"><input class="task-list-item-checkbox" disabled type="checkbox"> BB</li><li class="task-list-item"><input class="task-list-item-checkbox" disabled type="checkbox"> CC<ol class="contains-task-list"><li class="task-list-item"><input class="task-list-item-checkbox" checked disabled type="checkbox"> <strong>DD</strong></li><li class="task-list-item"><input class="task-list-item-checkbox" disabled type="checkbox"> FF</li></ol></li></ol><div class="note info">            <p>Task list는 텍스트 서식 적용이 가능합니다.</p>          </div>]]></content>
      
      
